snippet.title: LV99: Final Fortress — out now!
snippet.description:
Venture straight into the final dungeon of this heroic journey. Lay aside your legendary equipment for even better pieces. Slay bosses and super bosses with versatile skills and mighty finishers!

LV99: Final Fortress is out now! Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1321350/LV99_Final_Fortress

Website: https://www.greatpotiongames.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/greatpotiongames
